{
  "stem": "6526.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hey, to me-- give him-- hit me in the face and don't you-- I'll see you later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to get this, and this, and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let it be-- let it come to that, I'll be happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he'll give me that I'll-- with hard, and feeling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyhow, this helped me get, get the hands of that SS man off me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I did get a few lashes, and I got some other lashes on other places where we worked, because the work wasn't satisfactory, not fast enough.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they, they-- many reasons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Lagischa, I was so down that it came in another transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other transport took us-- we didn't know where it was taking us, but at least-- whatever's going to be was going to be.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took us to another-- to another camp called Buna, Monowitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a paradise for--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was-- the first week or 10 days, we were walked around in the camp, we didn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just ate and stayed--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave us food, and we stayed-- most of the time, we stayed with the kitchen, finished the cooking to, to bring back the, the, the, the barrels of food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also we used to lick him out to get more food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when they gave out, they had to be cleaned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to clean them, and this was food galore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went to work in-- In Buna, we went to work to the-- for the Carbide Werke, carbide producing--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, carbide is not ammunition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Carbide is-- no is this coal, like white coal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You put it in water, and it gives out gas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
